RICHIE:
♪ It was a graveyard smash ♪

24:07.046 --> 24:08.480
♪ He did the mash ♪

24:08.580 --> 24:10.139
♪ It caught on in a flash ♪

24:10.249 --> 24:11.808
♪ The monster mash ♪

24:11.917 --> 24:14.477
♪ He did the monster mash ♪

24:14.586 --> 24:17.487
♪ The zombies were having fun ♪

24:17.589 --> 24:21.219
♪ The party had just begun ♪

24:21.327 --> 24:24.820
♪ The guests included Wolf man ♪

24:24.930 --> 24:27.865
♪ Dracula and his son ♪

24:29.168 --> 24:30.329
♪ Now, everything's cool ♪

24:30.436 --> 24:32.530
♪ Drac's a part of the band ♪

24:32.638 --> 24:36.233
♪ And now the monster mash
is the hit of the land ♪

24:36.342 --> 24:39.403
♪ For you, the living,
this dance was meant, too ♪

24:39.511 --> 24:43.243
♪ When you get to my door,
tell them Peter sent you ♪

24:43.349 --> 24:44.248
POTSIE and RALPH:
♪ And do the mash... ♪

24:44.350 --> 24:46.375
FONZIE:
Hey, this is my costume.

24:46.485 --> 24:48.579
Plant your lips on Gene Kelly.

24:48.687 --> 24:50.246
I love kissin' in the rain.

24:50.356 --> 24:51.915
POTSIE and RALPH:
♪ The mash ♪

24:52.024 --> 24:53.924
RICHIE:
♪ It caught on in a flash ♪

24:54.026 --> 24:55.187
♪ The monster mash ♪

24:55.294 --> 24:57.388
♪ Yes, do the monster mash ♪

24:57.496 --> 25:00.727
♪ The monster mash. ♪

25:00.833 --> 25:02.824
(cheering and applause)

25:07.773 --> 25:10.105
♪ Good-bye, gray sky,
hello, blue ♪

25:10.209 --> 25:12.769
♪ There's nothing can hold me
when I hold you ♪

25:12.878 --> 25:15.347
♪ It feels so right,
it can't be wrong ♪

25:15.447 --> 25:17.882
♪ Rockin' and rollin'
all week long ♪

